Q8\ what is the version of BASH in your system?
A8\ $printf "%s\n" $BASH_VERSION
    or 
    $bash --version

Q9\write Hello world program in Bash
A9\ $echo "Hello World"

Q10\ Run the Program 
A10\ $mousepad hello.sh
     Typing inside the hello.sh 
     echo "Hello World"
     $chmod +x hello.sh
     $./hello.sh
